OL,3,CSchool sent into lockdown after former
OL,4,Cpupil 'assaulted three teachers'
OL,6,FA former pupil reportedly assaulted
OL,7,Fthree teachers after coming onto the
OL,8,Fschool's site, causing pupils to go go
OL,9,Finto lockdown.
OL,11,FThe incident happened at Newport High
OL,12,FSchool on Tuesday (7th January).
OL,14,FA former key stage three pupil came
OL,15,Fonto the school site and staff began
OL,16,Femergency procedures including a
OL,17,Flockdown towards the end of the school
OL,18,Fday, the school said in a statement on
OL,19,Fsocial media.
