OL,6,FGwent Police attended the school and
OL,7,Fsaid the ex-pupil "reportedly caused
OL,8,Fdamage to school property, cars and
OL,9,Fassaulted three teachers."
OL,11,F"Two teachers received minor injuries
OL,12,Fand the third attended hospital as a
OL,13,Fprecaution," they said.
OL,15,FThe school said: "Following an
OL,16,Fincident when a former key stage three
OL,17,Fpupil came onto the school site, staff
OL,18,Finstigated its emergency procedures to
OL,19,Fensure the safety of pupils.
