OL,3,CSchool sent into lockdown after former
OL,4,Cpupil 'assaulted three teachers'
OL,6,F"This included a lockdown procedure
OL,7,Ftowards the end of the school day.
OL,8,FPolice attended and supported the
OL,9,Fschool.
OL,11,F"Due to the ongoing investigation, we
OL,12,Fcannot comment further on the details
OL,13,Fon the incident, but it was extremely
OL,14,Fupsetting for both staff and pupils,
OL,15,Fparticularly those who witnessed the
OL,16,Fincident.
OL,18,F"We are aware of a rumour that a knife
OL,19,Fwas involved but at this stage we have
OL,20,Fno evidence that was the case and can
OL,21,Fconfirm that no weapons were used.
